series_spotlight.title: Series Spotlight
series_spotlight.description: Classic comedies, binge-worthy dramas, wild reality shows and more

701214.title: The Hunters
701214.description: Paxton and Tripp, two brothers, set out to find a secret artifact and help save their parents from a band of crossbow-carrying bad guys.

711653.title: TMZ Presents: Lamar Odom: Sex, Drugs & Kardashians
711653.description: NBA great Lamar Odom gets candid about his sex addiction, drug use and overdose—and how his downfall torpedoed his marriage to Khloe Kardashian.

0300007844.title: Braceface
0300007844.description: Alicia Silverstone stars as the voice of Sharon Spitz, aka Braceface, whose magical braces help her make the leap from middle school to high school!

0300010104.title: LA's Finest
0300010104.description: A former DEA agent with a complicated past gets partnered with a working mom when she takes a new job as an LAPD detective in this Bad Boys spinoff.

0300009901.title: Lovecraft Country
0300009901.description: Atticus Freema joins his friend Letitia and his uncle George to embark on a road trip across 1950's Jim Crow America in search of his missing father.

0300004985.title: Midsomer Murders
0300004985.description: A married veteran Detective Chief Inspector and his young sergeant investigate murders in the quaint, quirky villages of England’s Midsomer County.

0300009401.title: Running Wild with Bear Grylls
0300009401.description: Famed survivalist Bear Grylls takes six celebrities into the most remote and wild locations around the world for a 48-hour journey of a lifetime.

0300008596.title: Birds of Prey
0300008596.description: After Batman leaves New Gotham City, It’s up to Barbara Gordon aka Batgirl, Helena The Huntress, and a metahuman named Dinah to save the day.

02195.title: Relic Hunter
02195.description: The classic action series starring Tia Carrere as a fierce black belt and professor traveling the world to restore mythical artifacts and relics.

03936.title: The Joy of Painting With Bob Ross
03936.description: With his trademark soothing demeanor and delicate brush strokes, mellow artist Bob Ross guides viewers through his creative process.

0300007632.title: Class
0300007632.description: From the BBC and the Universe of Doctor Who. Like all teenagers, the students at Coal Hill Academy have hidden secrets and desires. They are facing their own worst fears, navigating a life of friends, parents, school, sex, sorrow - and possibly the end of existence. The very walls of space and time are starting to thin. Something is pressing on the other side: something waiting for its chance to kill everyone and everything, to bring us all into Shadow. Fear is coming. Tragedy is coming. War is coming.

0300007025.title: Maggie and the Ferocious Beast
0300007025.description: The constantly fun adventures of a six-year-old girl are endless as she makes new friends and goes new places with a fussy pig and a kind beast.

0300008046.title: Sanford
0300008046.description: Redd Foxx is back as his classic "Sanford and Son" character, in the story of him taking on two partners and meeting a wealthy Beverly Hills widow.

0300006793.title: Antiques Roadshow
0300006793.description: Everyday people bring out their extraordinary treasures for experts to examine. Who will bring a pricey artifact that will change their life forever?

0300006625.title: Charlie's Angels
0300006625.description: Three smart, stunning women use their lethal feminine charms and combat skills as PIs, assigned to crack cases via speakerphone by a mysterious boss.

03587.title: I Survived
03587.description: Ordinary people in deadly circumstances, from nightmarish abductions to shocking accidents, tell the incredible stories of how they survived.

0300010291.title: Say Yes to the Dress: Atlanta
0300010291.description: Southern brides look for the perfect gown for their big day at one of the biggest and bustling bridal salons in the United States, Bridals by Lori.

0300008010.title: Wife Swap UK
0300008010.description: A social experiment that makes spouses out of perfect strangers as two women switch homes for a week and assume each other’s roles as wife and mother.

0300008637.title: Mike Tyson Mysteries
0300008637.description: The adult animation classic series featuring the voice talents of Mike Tyson and Norm MacDonald sees the champion boxer taking on weekly mysteries!

03656.title: Meteor
03656.description: Two massive rocks, tumbling debris older than the solar system itself, collide in space. The course has been altered and the target is Earth.

02044.title: Flavor of Love
02044.description: 20 different women line up to date rapper Flavor Flav and win his heart, but first they must compete for quality time by taking on various challenges.

0300010409.title: Taken
0300010409.description: While dealing with a personal tragedy that shakes his world, CIA agent Bryan Mills fights to overcome the incident and exact revenge.

02370.title: This Old House
02370.description: This Old House is the No. 1 home enthusiast brand, offering trusted information and expert advice through award-winning television

0300009032.title: The Millionaire Matchmaker
0300009032.description: Money can't buy love, but in LA, it can buy the service of the world’s most elite matchmaker, plus her team of stylists, therapists, and date coaches.

0300010072.title: Bachelor in Paradise
0300010072.description: Some of the biggest stars from The Bachelor and The Bachelorette return for a second chance to find their soul mates—this time, in paradise.

0300008051.description: Regina King, Marla Gibbs, and Jackée Harry are comedy gold in this family sitcom about life in a middle-class apartment building in Washington, D.C.

03655.title: Moby Dick
03655.description: The only survivor of a lost whaling ship tells the stunning story of Captain Ahab's self-destructive, obsessive quest for a fabled white whale.

0300010313.title: Cupcake Wars
0300010313.description: Four cupcake bakers strive for the best taste and presentation as they compete to showcase their cupcakes at a major event and win a $10,000 prize.

0300008659.title: Queen of Swords
0300008659.description: Set in the 19th-century, this is the story of a young woman who returns to California following her father's death and joins the fight for justice.

04844.title: The New Scooby-Doo Mysteries
04844.description: Ruh-roh! Scooby-Doo, Scrappy, and the Mystery Machine gang are together again to solve a new batch of exciting, spooky, and brain-puzzling mysteries.

0300000125.title: Welcome Back, Kotter
0300000125.description: This series follows teacher Gabe Kotter as he returns to his former high school to teach a remedial class of students known as the “Sweathogs.”

03685.title: 60 Days In
03685.description: Innocent volunteers are sent to prison for 60 days, without officers or inmates knowing their secret, offering an unfiltered look at life behind bars.

03046.title: Unsolved Mysteries With Robert Stack
03046.description: Re-enactments, interviews, and updates provide clues and answers to real mysteries, from unsolved crimes to missing people and paranormal events.

0300010304.title: My Cat from Hell
0300010304.description: Cat behaviorist Jackson Galaxy helps families on the verge of giving up their felines with taming techniques to reverse a host of headstrong habits.

0300007812.title: Gordon Ramsay's 24 Hours to Hell and Back
0300007812.description: Celebrity chef Gordon Ramsay and his second-in-command have just 24 hours to bring struggling restaurants back from the brink of disaster.

0300008258.title: Los Pitufos (Doblado)
0300008258.description: En un bosque misterioso viven estos pequeños personajes azules que deben ingeniárselas para que el malvado brujo Gargamel y su gato no los atrapen.

0300005924.title: The Mix
0300005924.description: Join Tameka “Tiny” Harris for a high energy talk show from the perspective of its millennial host where no topic is off limits.

0300010292.title: The Little Couple
0300010292.description: Standing at under four feet tall, newlyweds Jennifer and Bill boldly face an average-size world in their missions to build a home and start a family.

0300005831.title: Ultimate Tag
0300005831.description: Competitors must vault, dodge, tumble, and dive, as they make their way through several different, challenging, three-dimensional obstacle courses.

0300010324.title: The Haunted
0300010324.description: Pet parents recount their animals' chilling experiences with ghosts, demons and other paranormal phenomena happening in their households.

0300005291.title: Danger 5
0300005291.description: Set in a dystopian version of the year 1982, five spies set out to kill Adolf Hitler before he kills them to achieve world domination by Christmas.

0300009454.title: The Colour of Magic
0300009454.description: An incompetent wizard involuntarily becomes the guide to the Discworld's first ever tourist, naive optimist Twoflower, and his magical wooden luggage.

03911.title: Celebrity Ghost Stories
03911.description: Famous personalities, from Carrie Fisher and Traci Lords to Joan Rivers and John Waters, reveal startling and personal paranormal experiences.

04430.title: Haven
04430.description: Crime series with supernatural shadings as an FBI agent assigned to a case in Maine finds herself on the trail of unexplained and spooky occurrences.

0300008096.title: The Dick Van Dyke Show
0300008096.description: Laugh along to one of television's most beloved shows, centering on a TV comedy writer, his charming wife, and goofy office colleagues.

0300008198.title: Are We There Yet?
0300008198.description: A divorced mother marries a former athlete, creating a hilarious and often chaotic blended household, where squabbles are always overcome by love.

04294.title: Dance Moms
04294.description: Popular reality series following the tough love teaching by a dance instructor-choreographer of talented tweens and her occasional parental run-ins.

0300009670.title: HouseBroken
0300009670.description: "HouseBroken" is an irreverent animated series following a group of neighborhood animals who help each other navigate the complicated life of being a pet.

02040.title: Fear Factor
02040.description: In each pulse-racing episode, contestants recruited across the country battle in extreme stunts designed to challenge the contestants both physically and mentally.

0300008167.title: Bad Girls Club
0300008167.description: A group of women with anger and control issues come together and try to improve themselves. But moving forward isn’t going to be easy.

03678.title: Category 7: The End of the World
03678.description: To stop a civilization-ending superstorm, a courageous professor and FEMA chief must venture into the dark heart of the swirling chaos.

04718.title: LEGO Ninjago Masters of Spinjitzu
04718.description: Peace has returned to Ninjago, but the four ninja warriors swear to protect and learn to master their Golden Weapons awaiting Lord Garmadon's return.

03647.title: 24 to Life
03647.description: The newly convicted struggle with the startling consequences of their crimes, for themselves and their families, in their last 24 hours of freedom.

0300004999.title: Garfield and Friends
0300004999.description: Lazy, lasagna-loving cat Garfield has fun adventures with his pal Odie and owner Jon.

0300006624.title: I Dream of Jeannie
0300006624.description: A marooned astronaut finds a strange bottle on an island containing a beautiful Genie whose granted wishes, back at home, don’t quite come out right!

0300008052.title: What's Happening!!
0300008052.description: Classic ‘70s series about L.A. high school journalist Raj and his best friends Rerun and Dwayne whose antics are never unseen by his nosy sister Dee.

0300009405.title: Slime Wars
0300009405.description: In this slime crafting competition show, three contestants battle to make the best slime creation.

03909.title: The World Wars
03909.description: Historical documentary that tracks the assassination in Sarajevo that sparked World War I up through the next global battle that was World War II.

0300009731.title: The Red Green Show
0300009731.description: This series follows hapless handyman Red Green as he welcomes viewers to Canada, where he and other colorful characters film a do-it-yourself TV show.

0300007078.title: Soap
0300007078.description: A satire on soap operas, this zany comedy threw together a group of family members whose lives were larger than life and never dull! Stories take some bizarre and unexpected turns as the daily living of the wealthy Tate family and the blue-collar Campbell family unfold.

03649.title: Bordertown: Laredo
03649.description: The Laredo police wage war against ruthless Mexican drug cartels, resorting to any means to transport illegal narcotics across the border.

02348.title: Duck Dynasty
02348.description: Follow the Robertsons as they run a multi-million dollar sporting empire and face everything from beavers to business deals, in this reality series.

0300005165.title: Divorce Court
0300005165.description: Judge Star Jones is the new face of Divorce Court presiding with her wisdom & experience. Join this new era through tears, laughter, truth & realness!

0300008303.title: Gimme a Break!
0300008303.description: A widowed, overworked police captain with three rambunctious daughters matches wits with a feisty housekeeper, who enforces law and order at home.

0300008580.title: Real Husbands of Hollywood
0300008580.description: Kevin Hart and his friends parody their own lives, where the pressures of spousal stardom are almost too much to handle, in this faux-reality satire.

0300010044.title: Whose Line Is It Anyway? Australia
0300010044.description: A hilarious lineup of performers are forced to navigate insane improv situations in this comedy game show based on the British hit of the same name.

0300009966.title: The Twilight Zone
0300009966.description: In this revival of the classic anthology series, host Forest Whitaker leads us on a mysterious journey into the deepest recesses of the human psyche.

0300007766.title: Sisters Inc.
0300007766.description: A series that helps show the challenges and possibilities for Black women in the 21st century as they accelerate their entrepreneurial endeavors.

0300007797.title: Project Runway All Stars
0300007797.description: Fashion designers from past episodes show off their style, as they come back to compete for another chance to be the winner of Project Runway.

0300008457.title: The Jeffersons
0300008457.description: Class, race, neighbors, family, and all kinds of clashes make for classic comedy in this beloved series about a family’s move on up to luxury living.

0300008639.title: The Steve Harvey Show
0300008639.description: Steve Harvey's sitcom from the WB network is classic '90s comedy about a musician-turned-teacher who teaches his unruly students a thing or three!

03688.title: Paranormal Cops
03688.description: After their shift ends, these Chicago cops spend their nights investigating paranormal activity, using detective work to separate fact from fiction.

0300005692.title: Day 5
0300005692.description: A group of survivors struggle to stay awake because sleep is now lethal. Battling fatigue and staying alert are essential to stay alive.

0300008260.title: Case Closed - Detective Conan (Dubbed)
0300008260.description: A high school detective is attacked by two mysterious men who force him to eat a pill that causes him to transform into a 7-year-old.

0300000124.title: Gilligan's Island
0300000124.description: Shipwrecked on an uncharted South Pacific island, seven castaways struggle to survive the outdoors—and each other—in this wacky classic comedy series.

0300008426.title: King
0300008426.description: After she is brought on as the lead detective of a major crime task force, a woman tackles leading a series of complicated investigations.

02166.title: Merlin
02166.description: The young wizard Merlin must keep his talent hidden in a kingdom where magic is banned as he and the future King Arthur face their destinies.

0300009902.title: Southland
0300009902.description: When a seasoned cop is assigned to train a rookie, his no-nonsense approach makes the young man question if he has what it takes to become an officer.

0300008442.title: ALF
0300008442.description: The hit ‘80s comedy about a furry alien life form – ALF – who crashes into a suburban family’s house and takes his place there as a total smart-aleck.

04765.title: I Can See Your Voice
04765.description: Contestants compete to win a cash prize if they can tell the difference between good and bad singers, without ever hearing them sing.

0300006054.title: Tea-G-I-F
0300006054.description: Dish Nation's, Blogger, Funky Dineva and Al Reynolds are dishing the latest celebrity gossip with Claudia.

0300006058.title: The Client List
0300006058.description: Jennifer Love Hewitt stars as Riley, a newly single mother who accepts employment at a day spa which offers some scandalous services.

0300007928.title: Extreme E: Electric Odyssey
0300007928.description: Extreme E is a radical new concept of electric SUV racing, in the most remote corners of the planet.

0300008618.title: Criminal Justice
0300008618.description: This series follows individuals as they are sent through the criminal justice system, where dangerous truths slowly come to light.

0300008984.title: Da Vinci’s Demons
0300008984.description: Tortured young genius, artist, and inventor, Leonardo Da Vinci, defies authority and throws himself into the future, changing the fate of humanity.

0300005636.title: The Fall
0300005636.description: The acclaimed crime series about a grim and gripping battle of wits between a brazen serial killer and a top-notch detective out to stop him.

0300010302.title: Too Cute!
0300010302.description: This series tells the coming-of-age stories of cuddly baby animals, from their wobbly first steps to their first venture into the outside world.

0300009893.title: Signal (Subbed)
0300009893.description: A detective from the '90s is connected with a modern day profiler through an old walkie-talkie, giving them a stronger shot at solving cold cases.

0300006385.title: Tales of the City
0300006385.description: The groundbreaking and beloved original saga about a naive Midwestern young woman who moves to the wild and liberated San Francisco of the 1970s.

0300006855.title: Scooby-Doo and Scrappy-Doo
0300006855.description: Everyone’s favorite mystery-solving Great Dane is here to find clues, along with a little help from his energetic nephew and four human companions.

0300010091.title: Kitchen Commando
0300010091.description: Chef Andre Rush brings the might of the military to restaurants across America as he takes up the mission to save the struggling service industry.

04893.title: McGraw Avenue
04893.description: In a notorious Detroit neighborhood, two men with different goals navigate the streets and deal with complex characters, to both survive and dominate.

0300005166.title: War Stories With Oliver North
0300005166.description: Documentary series featuring many overseas combat experiences of both the military forces and those citizens assisted, from WWII to 2005.

0300007283.title: The Slap
0300007283.description: Award-winning original adaptation of the story about the legal and personal trials that occur when a man slaps a child at a cookout who is not his.

0300009344.title: MasterChef
0300009344.description: Returning contestants vie for the top prize as MasterChef reopens its doors to some of the most memorable cooks in the competition’s history.

0300010244.title: Miami Vice
0300010244.description: From executive producer Michael Mann comes the explosive, groundbreaking detective show that redefined the word "cool” in the mid-1980s.

0300007971.title: Joe Millionaire
0300007971.description: When a 28-year old heavy equipment operator disguises himself as a millionaire, 20 hopeful young women jump at the chance to become his girlfriend.

0300010053.title: Fantasy Island (2021 Series)
0300010053.description: This modern drama series takes place at a luxury resort, where any fantasy requested by guests is fulfilled—although they rarely turn out as expected.

0300007799.title: Blue Mountain State
0300007799.description: Three new athletes on a top college football team learn the extreme high and low of being among the chosen few who are worshiped and tested on campus.

0300000007.title: Farmer Wants a Wife
0300000007.description: This series follows four hard-working farmers in search of real, lasting love.

0300000158.title: Hemlock Grove
0300000158.description: As a once-vibrant and now struggling community’s secrets begin to unravel, Hemlock Grove forces us to ask: What is the true nature of a monster?

0300008702.title: Buck Rogers
0300008702.description: A 20th Century pilot and his young friend buddy awake from 500 years of suspended animation.

0300010374.title: Paranormal Lockdown
0300010374.description: In this reality series, Nick Groff and Katrina Weidman investigate paranormal activity in purportedly haunted locations while hoping to capture proof.

0300009738.title: Sister, Sister
0300009738.description: Identical twins, separated at birth and adopted by different families, finally meet and try to bring their two very different parents together.

0300006868.title: Fantasy Island
0300006868.description: Dreams come true, for better or worse, in a tropical paradise, where a charming, enigmatic host and his diminutive assistant guide your magical visit.

0300008306.title: Next Level Chef
0300008306.description: Celebrity chef Gordon Ramsay hosts ambitious chefs facing unique cooking challenges, in a culinary competition to be the food world’s next superstar.

0300008427.title: What's Happening Now!!
0300008427.description: Raj, Rerun, Dwayne, and Shirley return in this hit sequel series that finds them in their 20s, Raj married, and sister Dee making guest appearances!

0300007162.title: Hotel Hell
0300007162.description: Gordon Ramsay travels the U.S.A. to give clueless hotel, B&B, and inn owners some grumpy hell of his own over dead bugs, gross sheets, dust, and more!

0300008354.title: Airwolf
0300008354.description: A crack test pilot from an elite government intel group flies a supersonic aerial weapon on top secret missions that bypass congressional approval.

0300006342.title: Shameless
0300006342.description: In the Gallagher home, chaos is king, as the unconventional family runs through endless scams, affairs, and petty crimes throughout Manchester.

0300010375.title: Invasion
0300010375.description: In this suspenseful tale, a blended family finds themselves at the center of a conspiracy designed to mask a massive alien takeover.

0300006628.title: Hart to Hart
0300006628.description: Wealthy, amorous, stylish supersleuths Jonathan and Jennifer Hart, roam the world, hobnob with the rich and famous, and solve crimes along the way

0300010393.title: Extreme Couponing
0300010393.description: These shoppers are everyday people who are after the most extraordinary deals, turning their money-saving skills into a fine art—and an obsession.

0300009492.title: Kitchen Nightmares en Español
0300009492.description: El célebre chef Gordon Ramsay visita restaurantes con problemas en los Estados Unidos y pasa una semana intentando ayudarles a tener éxito.

0300006728.title: Columbo
0300006728.description: This beloved series features the brilliant bumbling detective who despite his easygoing nature, always manages to crack the case.

03924.title: Intervention
03924.description: Emmy-Award winning series of profiles in addiction, with backstories and the current crisis that brings about family intervention and hope in rehab.

0300006283.title: Name That Tune
0300006283.description: Music-obsessed contestants face off in this exciting game show, as they try to identify popular songs with just a few notes for generous cash prizes.

0300007906.title: The Fix
0300007906.description: Long after she spectacularly failed to get a conviction of a celebrity-turned-murderer, a lawyer returns 8 years later when he allegedly kills again.

0300005117.title: Deal or No Deal
0300005117.description: This exciting game show has contestants play for a highly coveted cash prize in a tournament which requires nerve, talent, and a bit of luck.

0300007638.title: Life
0300007638.description: Created by multi-award-winning writer Mike Bartlett, Life explores the human capacity for connection in an increasingly splintered society. Manchester, England. The residents of a large suburban house go about their very different lives. The walls that divide their flats keep them apart. But life has a way of bringing people together. Like all ordinary lives, theirs are filled with the extraordinary. And as their stories begin to intersect, hidden secrets connect these characters in ways that could never have been anticipated.

0300006608.title: Bewitched
0300006608.description: The beloved TV series about a beautiful witch who marries an executive and starts a family as a housewife, much to the dismay of her powerful mother.

0300008367.title: Joe Millionaire: For Richer or Poorer
0300008367.description: Twenty women are faced with the age-old dilemma of choosing love or money while dating one prince and one pauper—without knowing which is which.

0300008705.title: Arctic Air
0300008705.description: This is a TV series about an extended family's unconventional relationships and intrigue as they run their airline in Yellowknife, Canada.

01546.title: Wolfblood
01546.description: Being a teen is hard but being a Wolfblood is even more complicated as Maddy and the others try to keep their shape-shifting secret from the world.

0300008146.title: The Returned
0300008146.description: In a French Alpine village, a random group of people realize that they’ve been dead for several years. Soon, devastating secrets emerge.

0300006856.title: The Flintstones
0300006856.description: Laugh along with the classic misadventures of two modern-day Stone Age families living amongst dinosaurs, doing their best in prehistoric times.

0300007403.title: The Border
0300007403.description: In a post-9/11 world of terrorism, drug trafficking and abducted children, the elite task force of Immigration and Customs Security holds the line.

0300008432.title: The Oblongs
0300008432.description: An eccentric family lives downstream from a toxic waste site, and finds that life is always presenting a series of unusual challenges for them.

0300008079.title: The Bernie Mac Show
0300008079.description: Bernie Mac stars as a stand up comic who, alongside his businesswoman wife, must take in his sister's three kids while she's in rehab.

0300006015.title: Hollywood Unlocked with Jason Lee Uncensored
0300006015.description: Host Jason Lee interviews celebrity guests to get UNCENSORED about the world of entertainment.

04829.title: The 13 Ghosts of Scooby-Doo
04829.description: When everyone’s favorite mystery solving Great Dane opens a mysterious box, he accidentally unleashes a series of frightening spirits.

0300008430.title: How the West Was Won
0300008430.description: A Virginia-based family leaves their home to bravely travel across the country and make a new life in the wild, untamed American West.

0300008875.title: The Island: Season 1 (Dubbed)
0300008875.description: After a deadly virus takes down a small community living on an island in the North Sea, the few survivors left must fight for their lives.

0300010071.title: Babylon 5
0300010071.description: 2258 CE. The lone space station Babylon 5 stands as the last and best hope for peace between a hundred worlds, alien and human alike.

0300005995.title: Beat Shazam
0300005995.description: Contestants race against the clock to identify hit songs and win $1 million dollars.

0300008571.title: The Player
0300008571.description: An ex-Fed-turned-security expert is recruited by a mysterious Vegas pit boss to prevent crimes while the rich place bets on his chances of success.

03837.title: Flood
03837.description: When rising waters threaten the lives of millions in London, marine engineers race against the clock to save the city from total devastation.

0300006821.title: Ambitions
0300006821.description: Two top Atlanta lawyers compete in personal and professional endeavors, in a battle of ambitions that so often gets out of control.

02914.title: Forensic Files
02914.description: Witnesses, investigators and medical experts lend their unique perspective on true crime in every episode of this long-running docuseries.

03697.title: V
03697.description: When human-looking aliens known as Visitors appear in every major city U.S. promoting peace, an FBI counter-terrorist discovers their deadly plot.

03054.title: True Tori
03054.description: Follow Tori Spelling in real-time as she searches for honesty and happiness with her husband Dean after one of the most devastating chapters of her life.

0300006869.title: Fantasy Island (1998 Series)
0300006869.description: The darker reboot of the popular series features more intricate stories of visitors to the magical island, who seek resolution to ethical problems.

0300007917.title: Secrets and Lies
0300007917.description: Juliette Lewis stars as a determined and brilliant detective whose latest murder case challenges her and her team with a family’s secrets and lies.

0300007896.title: The Freak Brothers
0300007896.description: After smoking a magical strain of weed and falling into a 50-year slumber, the Freak Brothers and their outspoken cat awaken in the 2020s and attempt to adjust to the bizarre rat race of modern times.

0300005214.title: LEGO Masters
0300005214.description: LEGO enthusiasts participate in a series of competitions that start with a single LEGO brick and culminate with inspiring, complex constructions.

0300000159.title: Hannibal
0300000159.description: An FBI investigator with the ability to empathize with psychopaths is assigned to work with renowned psychiatrist—and secret cannibal—Hannibal Lecter.

0300009383.title: Too Close for Comfort
0300009383.description: Henry, a conservative cartoonist, and Muriel, a freelance photographer, are owners of a two-unit house, where they live with their two daughters.

0300009559.title: Farscape
0300009559.description: Thrown into a distant part of the universe, an Earth astronaut finds himself part of a fugitive alien starship crew.

0300008958.title: Bonanza
actors: Lorne Greene Pernell Roberts Dan Blocker Michael Landon Guy Williams
0300008958.description: On their 1,000-square mile Ponderosa Ranch in late-1850’s Nevada, Ben Cartwright and his three sons defend their land, business and fellow citizenry.

02081.title: My Crazy Ex
02081.description: This docu-reality series tells the extraordinary but true stories of relationships that went awry when one partner’s behavior morphed from romantic to excessive to extreme.

01939.title: The Dead Zone
01939.description: Based on characters from the Stephen King novel, a young man awakens from a coma with extraordinary psychic powers, after suffering a tragic car accident.

03744.title: Tin Man
03744.description: It’s a whole new yellow brick road as a mistress of evil with plans to come to Earth must face a rebellious, kind girl who sees visions in her dreams.

03577.title: Bring It
03577.description: A tough but fierce dance coach trains an elite group of hip-hop majorettes, the Dancing Dolls, to compete across their local region.

0337.title: McLeod's Daughters
0337.description: McLeod's Daughters tells the story of two sisters who are reunited when they inherit a vast outback cattle property in South Australia.

0300008098.title: NFL Top 10
0300008098.description: Get ready to break down the Top 10 NFL moments, across a variety of categories, along with interviews and archival video and audio of those plays.

0300006335.title: Detectorists
0300006335.description: Follow two oddball metal detectorists as they painstakingly plough through the literal and figurative tracks and fields of life in search of treasure.

0300007634.title: The First Team
0300007634.description: Starring six-time Emmy nominee Will Arnett and Chris Geere, this sharp character comedy follows the off-the-pitch escapades of three Premier League footballers.

04717.title: Cosmos: A Spacetime Odyssey
04717.description: Join acclaimed astrophysicist Neil deGrasse Tyson on a journey through space and time in an effort to discover humanity’s place within the universe.

0300007796.title: Project Runway
0300007796.description: Models and fashion icons judge the works of clothing designers in this intense reality competition series that showcases up-and-coming artists.

0300010073.title: The Bachelor
0300010073.description: One lucky man dates 15 women over the course of a few weeks in search of his dream woman—and hopefully bride-to-be—in this reality smash hit.

0300008048.title: Less Than Kind
0300008048.description: A 15-year-old outcast tries to blend in with his peers, but his self-destructive driving instructor father and pyromaniac mother aren’t much help.

0300008470.title: The Joy of Painting With Bob Ross (Español)
0300008470.description: El pintor de árboles felices nos muestra su técnica de mojado sobre mojado y nos anima a plasmar nuestros propios pincelazos sobre el lienzo.

0300009026.title: Queer Eye
0300009026.description: The Fab Five: a designer, a stylist, a chef, a beauty guru, and a "concierge of cool.” These gifted gay men give straight men a fun-filled makeover.

0300007922.title: Rowan & Martin's Laugh-In
0300007922.description: Join comedy duo Dan Rowan and Dick Martin in their classic sketch comedy series, which takes cues from vaudeville and rapid-fire satire.

0300007657.title: 800 Words
0300007657.description: A comfortable Australian journalist becomes a single father when his wife dies and soon decides to move with his two kids to New Zealand to regroup.

03320.title: Hell's Kitchen
03320.description: Renowned restauranteur Gordon Ramsay hosts a fierce competition for aspiring chefs, as they vie for a prestigious job at one of his eateries.

0300008959.title: NFL Explained
0300008959.description: A look at everything that goes into making the NFL what it is today, from the evolution of the NFL Rules to what goes into feeding an NFL team.

0300010052.title: Special Forces: World's Toughest Test
0300010052.description: This series follows celebrity contestants as they endure grueling challenges from the playbook of the actual Special Forces selection process.

03907.title: Billion Dollar Wreck
03907.description: Reality-documentary series from film director Michael Bay, where a treasure hunter keeps his quest to recover sunken gold coins from a 1909 shipwreck.

0300006872.title: Sheena
0300006872.description: ‘Baywatch’ star Gena Lee Nolin stars in this series as Sheena, Queen of the Jungle, whose magical powers are used to protect her animal kingdom.

0300010081.title: Nikita
0300010081.description: Betrayed by the secret government agency that made her an assassin, the charming and deadly Nikita makes it her mission to undermine the organization.

0300007970.title: Elite Youth
0300007970.description: America’s most sought-after high school basketball players and future NBA greats compete in the 2018 season of Nike's Elite Youth Basketball League.

0300006854.title: Scooby-Doo Where Are You?
0300006854.description: The classic adventures of the lovable Great Dane and his human companions as they hunt for clues, hungry for a solution to mysteries and a snack.

0300007032.title: 6teen
0300007032.description: This sharp and amusing mid-00s animated comedy follows the after-school lives of six 16 year-old mall-rats.

0300010307.title: Toddlers & Tiaras
0300010307.description: This series takes viewers behind the scenes into the cutthroat—and often controversial—world of child beauty pageants, where winning is everything.

0300000119.title: The Facts of Life
0300000119.description: Four teens, each with their own backgrounds and personalities, become inseparable friends when they’re brought together at Eastland Academy for girls.

0300007735.title: The Armstrong & Miller Show
0300007735.description: A wealth of great characters populate this sketch show that presents a veneer of respectability, which is often and hilariously punctured and cracked.

0300007418.title: The Almighty Johnsons
0300007418.description: The Johnsons are four ordinary Kiwi brothers who have inherited the powers of Norse Gods. But Norse Gods lived a long time ago, and over many generations, their powers have become diluted.

0300009777.title: Jules Verne's Mysterious Island
0300009777.description: A small family of castaways must battle to survive against untold terrors when their hot air balloon lands on an uncharted island.

0300007117.title: Crime Scene Kitchen
0300007117.description: Bakers must decode what type of dessert was made using just crumbs and a few elusive clues.

0300008574.title: Malcolm & Eddie
0300008574.description: A mid-1990’s odd couple story revolving around a carefree slob and tow truck operator and his preppy, neatfreak, aspiring sportscaster roommate.

0300010397.title: How It's Made
0300010397.description: This series explores the fascinating world of how everyday items are manufactured and produced—anything from toothpicks, to pantyhose, to gummy candy.

0300008156.title: The Take
0300008156.description: A ruthless ex-con, ordered to preserve a criminal empire for its incarcerated boss, faces a dilemma when his family gets involved and lands in danger.

0300006059.title: Kevin Can Wait
0300006059.description: A newly retired police officer has to reconsider his plans when his daughter announces she’s dropping out of college to support her fiancé.

0300009133.title: MasterChef UK
0300009133.description: Some of the best amateur cooks in Britain show off their technical skills and compete for the top spot by progressing through a series of challenges.

0300006767.title: Heartland
0300006767.description: Alberta sisters and their grandfather spend their years on the family ranch, where they must work through complicated issues together.

0300008356.title: Diff'rent Strokes
0300008356.description: Follows the lives of an unconventional family made up of a white millionaire widower, his daughter, and the adopted Black sons of his deceased maid.

04631.title: Degrassi: The Next Generation
04631.description: Long-running TV-series, acclaimed for its powerful realism in taking on the life-changing issues facing a group of friends at a Toronto high school.

03646.title: Little Women: Atlanta
03646.description: There's no shortage of excitement in this circle of friends as they face the daily challenges that come with being a little person in the big city.

0300009137.title: So You Think You Can Dance
0300009137.description: Skilled dancers showcase their talents in various dance styles while competing to be crowned America's favorite dancer.

0300005068.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares
0300005068.description: A brilliant chef who never holds his tongue, Gordon Ramsay visits struggling restaurants around the UK and shows them how to turn the ship around.

0300007764.title: Pokémon the Series: Black & White
0300007764.description: Ash and Pikachu are off to the distant Unova region, where they'll encounter new friends, new rivals, new challenges, and all-new Pokémon! Upon arrival, Ash meets aspiring Dragon Master Iris, full of spirit and determination, and Pokémon Connoisseur Cilan, who is always available to lend his expertise. Above all, Ash will need plenty of new Pokémon on his team if he wants to win Unova's tournaments and Gym badges. Following his every move is the criminal trio of Team Rocket, with sinister new schemes and a fresh resolve to catch Pikachu! Then there's the mysterious N...is he a friend or a foe, and what is his connection with the secret organization known as Team Plasma? And what is Team Plasma planning to do with one of the Legendary Pokémon of the Unova region? Once this adventure starts, the excitement won't stop!

0300010102.title: La Femme Nikita
0300010102.description: Condemned to death for a vicious crime she didn't commit, Nikita reluctantly chooses to live as an assassin for a secret government agency.

0300007629.title: Meet, Marry, Murder
0300007629.description: Wedded couples vow to stay together, until death do they part. This series looks at what happens when a bride or groom causes their beloved’s demise.

0300010083.title: The Tomorrow People
0300010083.description: A group of genetically advanced teens with paranormal abilities flee the agents of a paramilitary group on a mission to eradicate them.

0300008044.title: The Inbetweeners
0300008044.description: Four friends in public school enjoy their last years of shenanigans, as they prepare to face the real world in this hilarious series.

0300005163.title: The Masked Singer
0300005163.description: Celebrity performers, costumed to conceal their identities but dropping hints along the way, compete each week as one is eliminated and unmasked.

0300009900.title: Generation
0300009900.description: A group of high school students explore their identities and sexualities, challenging the antiquated social norms in their conservative community.

0300007907.title: Brickleberry
0300007907.description: Daniel Tosh stars as the lead voice in this Comedy Central cartoon series about a group of national park rangers who are terrible at their jobs.
